{%- assign accent = '#B07A4E' -%}
<main style="--world-color: {{ accent }};">
  <section class="pc-sub-hero">
    <div class="container pc-sub-hero__inner">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow pc-sub-hero__eyebrow">Postcard subscriptions</div>
        <h1 class="h-display pc-sub-hero__title">Set it.<br><span class="pc-sub-hero__title-em">Forget</span> it.<br>Save 15%.</h1>
        <p class="pc-sub-hero__body">The shampoo arrives the week you finish the last one. The hand wash refills before you notice. Your favourite scent shows up like clockwork &mdash; and you stop thinking about it.</p>
        <div class="pc-sub-hero__ctas">
          <a class="btn" href="/collections/subscribable">Browse subscribable products &rarr;</a>
          <a class="tlink" href="{{ routes.account_url }}">Already subscribed? Manage in your account</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-sub-hero__stack">
        <div class="pc-sub-postcard pc-sub-postcard--0" style="box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #C7A8D6;">
          <div class="pc-sub-postcard__row">
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__chip" style="background: #C7A8D6;"></div>
            <span class="postmark pc-sub-postcard__pm pc-sub-postcard__pm--cw"><div>MAR<br>&middot; 2026 &middot;<br>SG</div></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__cap">Delivery 1</div>
            <div class="h-typewriter pc-sub-postcard__from">From Hotel Lobby</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pc-sub-postcard pc-sub-postcard--1" style="box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #5C6688;">
          <div class="pc-sub-postcard__row">
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__chip" style="background: #5C6688;"></div>
            <span class="postmark pc-sub-postcard__pm pc-sub-postcard__pm--ccw"><div>JUN<br>&middot; 2026 &middot;<br>SG</div></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__cap">Delivery 2</div>
            <div class="h-typewriter pc-sub-postcard__from">From Moon Bloom</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pc-sub-postcard pc-sub-postcard--2" style="box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #6E8B5C;">
          <div class="pc-sub-postcard__row">
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__chip" style="background: #6E8B5C;"></div>
            <span class="postmark pc-sub-postcard__pm pc-sub-postcard__pm--cw"><div>SEP<br>&middot; 2026 &middot;<br>SG</div></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__cap">Delivery 3</div>
            <div class="h-typewriter pc-sub-postcard__from">From Java Jungle</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pc-sub-postcard pc-sub-postcard--3" style="box-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #E8B796;">
          <div class="pc-sub-postcard__row">
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__chip" style="background: #E8B796;"></div>
            <span class="postmark pc-sub-postcard__pm pc-sub-postcard__pm--ccw"><div>DEC<br>&middot; 2026 &middot;<br>SG</div></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="pc-sub-postcard__cap">Delivery 4</div>
            <div class="h-typewriter pc-sub-postcard__from">From Coconut Beach</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pc-sub-trust">
      <div class="container pc-sub-trust__inner">
        <div class="pc-sub-trust__item"><div class="h-display pc-sub-trust__h">Save 15%</div><div class="pc-sub-trust__n">every order, every time</div></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-trust__item"><div class="h-display pc-sub-trust__h">Free shipping</div><div class="pc-sub-trust__n">on subscription orders over S$40</div></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-trust__item"><div class="h-display pc-sub-trust__h">Skip, swap, pause</div><div class="pc-sub-trust__n">no questions, no fees</div></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-trust__item"><div class="h-display pc-sub-trust__h">Cancel anytime</div><div class="pc-sub-trust__n">in 2 clicks. We mean it.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pc-sub-how__head">
        <span class="pc-sub-how__pill" style="background: {{ accent }}22;">How it works</span>
        <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-how__title">Four small steps. One forever-shower.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-sub-how__grid">
        <div class="pc-sub-how__cell"><div class="pc-sub-how__chip" style="background: #C7A8D6;"></div><div class="h-display pc-sub-how__num">01</div><h3 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-how__h">Pick your products</h3><p class="pc-sub-how__p">Any of the 80+ subscribable items. Mix worlds. Mix categories.</p></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-how__cell pc-sub-how__cell--alt"><div class="pc-sub-how__chip" style="background: #5C6688;"></div><div class="h-display pc-sub-how__num">02</div><h3 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-how__h">Choose your cadence</h3><p class="pc-sub-how__p">30, 60, or 90 days. Skin first, hair second, scent third &mdash; set each one to its own rhythm.</p></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-how__cell"><div class="pc-sub-how__chip" style="background: #6E8B5C;"></div><div class="h-display pc-sub-how__num">03</div><h3 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-how__h">We post. You shower.</h3><p class="pc-sub-how__p">Box arrives 3 days before you run out, on average. Tracked, paper-only packaging.</p></div>
        <div class="pc-sub-how__cell pc-sub-how__cell--alt"><div class="pc-sub-how__chip" style="background: #FFB233;"></div><div class="h-display pc-sub-how__num">04</div><h3 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-how__h">Skip, swap, cancel</h3><p class="pc-sub-how__p">Anytime. From the email. From your phone. From your account. No call required.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section pc-sub-perks">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pc-sub-perks__head">
        <div class="eyebrow pc-sub-perks__eyebrow">The trade you make</div>
        <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-perks__title">You give us a habit. We give you back time, money, and one less thing to remember.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-sub-perks__grid">
        <div class="pc-sub-perk-card">
          <span class="postmark pc-sub-perk-card__pm" style="border-color: #FFB233; color: #FFB233;"><div>SET IT</div></span>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__tag" style="color: #FFB233;">Set it</div>
          <h3 class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__h">One less browser tab.</h3>
          <p class="pc-sub-perk-card__p">No more &ldquo;did I order shampoo?&rdquo; thoughts at 11pm. Pick once, set the cadence, walk away. Your future self stays clean and lightly perfumed.</p>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-block">
            <div class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__stat" style="color: #FFB233;">4.2</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-label">minutes saved per re-order</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pc-sub-perk-card">
          <span class="postmark pc-sub-perk-card__pm" style="border-color: #C7A8D6; color: #C7A8D6;"><div>FORGET IT</div></span>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__tag" style="color: #C7A8D6;">Forget it</div>
          <h3 class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__h">It arrives before you notice.</h3>
          <p class="pc-sub-perk-card__p">We watch your last order. By default, we ship a fresh batch 3 days before you typically run out. You can move that window &mdash; or just trust it.</p>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-block">
            <div class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__stat" style="color: #C7A8D6;">3 days</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-label">before you finish the last one</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pc-sub-perk-card">
          <span class="postmark pc-sub-perk-card__pm" style="border-color: #6E8B5C; color: #6E8B5C;"><div>SAVE 15%</div></span>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__tag" style="color: #6E8B5C;">Save 15%</div>
          <h3 class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__h">Loyalty paid in cash, not points.</h3>
          <p class="pc-sub-perk-card__p">15% off every subscription order, every time. Stacks with member tiers. Free shipping over S$40. The bottle that costs S$28 once costs you S$23.80 forever.</p>
          <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-block">
            <div class="h-display pc-sub-perk-card__stat" style="color: #6E8B5C;">15%</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-perk-card__stat-label">off every order, automatically</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--tight section">
    <div class="container pc-sub-noworries">
      <span class="postmark postmark--yellow pc-sub-noworries__pm"><div>NO<br>HOSTAGES<br>&middot;<br>POSTCARD<br>SG &middot; 26</div></span>
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">The fine print, in friendly typeface</div>
        <h2 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-noworries__title">Skip a month. Swap your world. Pause for a holiday. Cancel because you&rsquo;ve finally cleared your bathroom shelf.</h2>
        <p class="pc-sub-noworries__body">Two clicks from any email or your account dashboard. No phone tree, no &ldquo;we&rsquo;ll miss you&rdquo; gauntlet, no penalty for leaving and coming back. We treat your subscription like a houseplant: yours to water, yours to give away.</p>
        <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefits">
          <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit"><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-h">&#10003; Skip an order</div><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-n">Until your next cycle</div></div>
          <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit"><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-h">&#10003; Swap a world</div><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-n">Same product, new scent</div></div>
          <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit"><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-h">&#10003; Change cadence</div><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-n">Slower or faster, anytime</div></div>
          <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit"><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-h">&#10003; Pause indefinitely</div><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-n">Resume on a tap</div></div>
          <div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit"><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-h">&#10003; Cancel</div><div class="pc-sub-noworries__benefit-n">No questions asked</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section pc-sub-popular">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pc-sub-popular__head">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow" style="color: {{ accent }};">What 12,000+ subscribers ship monthly</div>
          <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-popular__title">The regulars.</h2>
        </div>
        <a class="tlink" href="/collections/subscribable">Browse all subscribable products &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-sub-popular__grid">
        {%- assign popular = 'Hotel Lobby Hand & Body Wash|Hotel Lobby|#C7A8D6|Every 60 days|2840|28~~Moon Bloom Body Wash|Moon Bloom|#5C6688|Every 60 days|1920|28~~Smoked Roses Shampoo|Smoked Roses|#8E4F5C|Every 90 days|1610|32~~Java Jungle Shampoo Bar|Java Jungle|#6E8B5C|Every 60 days|1480|18~~Bakuchiol Bay Serum|Bakuchiol Bay|#9CC4D6|Every 30 days|1240|64~~Coconut Beach Deo Stick|Coconut Beach|#E8B796|Every 60 days|980|22' | split: '~~' -%}
        {%- for entry in popular -%}
          {%- assign p = entry | split: '|' -%}
          {%- assign price = p[5] | times: 1 -%}
          {%- assign sub_price = price | times: 0.85 -%}
          <div class="pc-sub-popular-card">
            <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__rank">#{{ forloop.index }}</div>
            <div class="ph ph--world pc-sub-popular-card__media" style="--world-color: {{ p[2] }};">
              <span>{{ p[1] }}</span>
              <span class="postmark postmark--yellow pc-sub-popular-card__pm"><div>SAVE<br>&middot; 15% &middot;<br>SUB</div></span>
            </div>
            <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__body">
              <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__chip-row">
                <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__chip" style="background: {{ p[2] }};"></div>
                <div class="eyebrow">{{ p[1] }}</div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="h-typewriter pc-sub-popular-card__title">{{ p[0] }}</h3>
              <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__row">
                <div>
                  <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__caption">Most popular cadence</div>
                  <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__cadence">{{ p[3] }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__price-block">
                  <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__strike">S${{ price }}</div>
                  <div class="h-display pc-sub-popular-card__price" style="color: {{ accent }};">S${{ sub_price | round: 2 }}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="pc-sub-popular-card__subs">{{ p[4] }} active subscribers</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>

      <div class="pc-sub-discovery">
        <span class="postmark postmark--ink pc-sub-discovery__pm"><div>NEW<br>&middot; 26 &middot;<br>BOX</div></span>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">New: the Discovery subscription</div>
          <h3 class="h-display pc-sub-discovery__title">A different world, every quarter.</h3>
          <p class="pc-sub-discovery__body">Three travel-size products from a curated world, posted every 90 days. We pick. You discover. Cancel after one box if it&rsquo;s not for you.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn--ink" href="/products/discovery-subscription">From S$32/quarter &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pc-sub-compare__head">
        <div class="eyebrow">Subscription vs one-time, year on year</div>
        <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-compare__title">What it actually saves you.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pc-sub-compare__table">
        <div class="pc-sub-compare__head-row">
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__head-cell pc-sub-compare__head-cell--label">One-shower household, year of</div>
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__head-cell">One-time</div>
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__head-cell pc-sub-compare__head-cell--accent">
            <div class="pc-sub-compare__chip" style="background: {{ accent }};"></div>
            <span class="h-display">Subscription</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        {%- assign rows = 'Hand & body wash (refilled)|S$112|S$95.20~~Shampoo (refilled)|S$128|S$108.80~~Conditioner (refilled)|S$128|S$108.80~~Deodorant|S$132|S$112.20~~Anywhere fragrance|S$84|S$71.40~~Shipping (over S$40 → free on sub)|S$48|S$0' | split: '~~' -%}
        {%- for entry in rows -%}
          {%- assign r = entry | split: '|' -%}
          {%- assign mod = forloop.index | modulo: 2 -%}
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__row{% if mod == 0 %} pc-sub-compare__row--alt{% endif %}">
            <div class="pc-sub-compare__cell pc-sub-compare__cell--label">{{ r[0] }}</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-compare__cell">{{ r[1] }}</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-compare__cell" style="color: {{ accent }};">{{ r[2] }}</div>
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
        <div class="pc-sub-compare__total">
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__total-label">Annual total</div>
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__total-cell">S$632</div>
          <div class="pc-sub-compare__total-cell">
            <div class="h-display" style="color: {{ accent }};">S$496.40</div>
            <div class="pc-sub-compare__savings">You save S$135.60 / year</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="pc-sub-compare__footnote">Based on average household consumption &middot; refills count &middot; cancel anytime &middot; these maths never lie.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pc-sub-testimonial">
    <div class="container pc-sub-testimonial__inner">
      <div class="ph ph--world pc-sub-testimonial__photo" style="--world-color: #C7A8D6;"><span>customer &middot; portrait</span></div>
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">From Mei, subscriber since 2024</div>
        <p class="h-typewriter pc-sub-testimonial__quote">&ldquo;I forgot I had a Postcard subscription. Then the box landed. Then I remembered why I have it. Three years and I haven&rsquo;t bought shampoo from anywhere else.&rdquo;</p>
        <div class="pc-sub-testimonial__attribution">MEI L. &middot; 4 active subscriptions &middot; Hotel Lobby loyalist</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section pc-sub-faq">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-faq__title">The questions everyone asks.</h2>
      <div class="pc-pdp-faq__list">
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item" open><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">Is there a minimum commitment?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">None. You can cancel after your first delivery &mdash; no fees, no &ldquo;are you sure&rdquo; emails. We&rsquo;d rather you come back happy than stay reluctantly.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">What if I don&rsquo;t need it yet?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">Skip the next order from your dashboard or directly from the email we send 5 days before each ship date. You can skip indefinitely if you&rsquo;re running through last month&rsquo;s slowly.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">Can I subscribe to refills only?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">Yes &mdash; once you&rsquo;ve bought the bottle, the refill is what your subscription delivers. It costs less, it weighs less, and it counts toward free-shipping thresholds.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">Can I switch worlds within a subscription?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">Anytime. Same product, new scent, same cadence. Switch from Hotel Lobby to Moon Bloom in two clicks. Some subscribers rotate four worlds across the year.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">Does the 15% discount stack with member tiers?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">Yes. Wanderer gets 15% sub + 5% tier = 20%. Voyager gets 15% sub + 8% tier = 23%. Postmaster gets 15% sub + 10% tier = 25%. Plus the free shipping over S$40.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">What happens if my card fails?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">We try twice over 5 days, then email you to update. The order pauses &mdash; it doesn&rsquo;t cancel. You don&rsquo;t lose your subscriber status, your discount, or your custom blend.</p></details>
        <details class="pc-pdp-faq__item"><summary class="pc-pdp-faq__q">Will you upsell me to bigger sizes?</summary><p class="pc-pdp-faq__a">No. We&rsquo;ll suggest the right cadence based on your usage, and we&rsquo;ll surface relevant new products in your dashboard &mdash; but we don&rsquo;t auto-add anything. The box you set is the box you get.</p></details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pc-sub-cta">
    <div class="container container--narrow pc-sub-cta__inner">
      <div class="eyebrow">Begin your habit</div>
      <h2 class="h-display pc-sub-cta__title">One subscription.<br>One less errand.</h2>
      <p class="pc-sub-cta__body">Start with one product. Add more when you&rsquo;re ready. Cancel when you&rsquo;re done.</p>
      <div class="pc-sub-cta__ctas">
        <a class="btn btn--ink" href="/collections/subscribable">Browse subscribable products &rarr;</a>
        <a class="tlink pc-sub-cta__quiz" href="/pages/subscription-quiz">Or take the 2-min subscription quiz</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Subscriptions page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Subscriptions page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
